    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You emit powerful radiant energy from your body, channeling the power of the sun to burn your enemies.</em></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - Enemies in a 60 ft. Radius - 1 Minute - 1/Long Rest - Magical</p><p>When you use this ability, you begin emitting bright light in a 30 ft. radius and dim light in a 60 ft. radius, which counts as sunlight. When you use this ability, and again on each of your turns as a bonus action, you can deal damage to your enemies.</p><p><strong>Constitution Saving Throw</strong></p><p><strong>Failure:</strong> 20 radiant damage.</p><p><strong>Success:</strong> 10 radiant damage.</p>",
